@ENDNODE

@NODE "MISC_SUPPORT" "SUPPORT"
@TITLE "CrunchyDat - About"

About
~~~~~
We are a programmer-team from Germany who want to support the amiga with
QUALITY freeware programms.
As you can see by our FIRST product, we take this as an aim.
We consist of 5 peoples.

To contact us write to one of our addresses which will be released in
our next update/release. Sorry guys, be patient. At the moment we are
trying to get a P.O. Box -> but it isn't ready yet. :-(



@ENDNODE

